725206f-a.title: Queens: 31st Street - 30th Drive
725206f-a.text:
31st Street, east side, just north of 30th Drive, showing
the Second Church of Astoria, Reformed in America, in the shadow
of the I.R.T. 'E17, looking north.
View 2 is eastward across the ''El.''
P. L. Sperr  View 1: June 3, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: March 14, 1931

725205f-a.title: Queens: 31st Street - 30th Drive
725205f-a.text:
31st Street, at the N.W. corner of 30th Drive, showing
the Hellenic Orthodox Community Church of Astoria and St.
Demetrios. The view is northeastward from ies 30th Drive
toward 31st Street on which is the I.R.T.'g1.' Across the
latter appears the steeple of the Second Reformed Church of
Astoria.
View 2 is from the corner of 30th Street.
P. L. Sperr  March 14, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS
